Using `simplexml_load_string()` or `DOMDocument` without proper configuration is extremely dangerous and can lead to XML External Entity (XXE) attacks. By default, older PHP configurations allow external entity loading, enabling attackers to read arbitrary files from your server.

**VULNERABLE CODE**:

```php
